            innerHTML:
              '\u003cp>There’s plenty of eager chatter about what comes next: will it be a hybrid, \u003ca href="https://www.glassdoor.com/blog/companies-hiring-for-remote-roles/">remote\u003c/a>, or an in-person workplace? It feels like leaders are anxious to cue the next chapter-capitalizing on the new skills that employees honed while powering through a once-in-a-century crisis.\u003c/p>\n',
            innerContent:
              '\u003cp>There’s plenty of eager chatter about what comes next: will it be a hybrid, \u003ca href="https://www.glassdoor.com/blog/companies-hiring-for-remote-roles/">remote\u003c/a>, or an in-person workplace? It feels like leaders are anxious to cue the next chapter-capitalizing on the new skills that employees honed while powering through a once-in-a-century crisis.\u003c/p>\n',
